FBIS4-21755 "jptot014__l94055" JPRS-TOT-94-014-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 28 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA ALGERIA Foreign Ministry Official Assassinated in Algiers Suburb Foreign Ministry Official Assassinated in Algiers Suburb LD2803104194 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1000 GMT 28 Mar 94 LD2803104194 Algiers Radio Algiers Network Arabic BFN [Text] Security authorities have announced that Touati Belkacem, deputy director of the African section at the Foreign Ministry, was assassinated this morning in front of his home near Bordj El Kifan in the suburbs of the capital. The victim was attacked by three men armed with automatic pistols as he was preparing to leave his house. The same source added that his wife was wounded.
